Name: Mydei
Desc: Kremnos, the mist-shrouded city of chaos and war! Its royal lineage is tainted with patricide, and its god bears the name of calamity.\nThe undying Mydeimos, the lion apart from the rest. Chrysos Heir who seeks the Coreflame of Strife, must suffer a thousand deaths, be bathed in blood on the path home, and bear the madness of fate alone.\nâ€” Kingslayer be king, godslayer be god. Iron-hooves pound across the wilderness for the campaign, and must eventually soak in the blood of their homeland.

1.Name: Frost Hones Spine of Steel
1.Desc: Increases the DMG multiplier dealt by "Godslayer Be God" to the primary target by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>. This ability now deals to all enemies Imaginary DMG equal to the DMG multiplier dealt to the primary target.

2.Name: Strife Beholds Cry of Dead
2.Desc: During "Vendetta," the DMG dealt by Mydei ignores <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of enemy targets' DEF. After he receives healing, converts <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> of the healed amount to Charge. The tally of the converted Charge cannot exceed <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> point(s). Resets this tally of Charge after any unit takes action.

3.Name: Honor Exalts Feast of Faith
3.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nBasic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

4.Name: Siren Jolts the Laconic Lion
4.Desc: While in "Vendetta," increases CRIT DMG by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> and restores HP by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of this unit's Max HP after receiving attacks from enemy targets.

5.Name: War Chisels Flesh of Flame
5.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nTalent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.

6.Name: Legacy Scales Mound of Blood
6.Desc: When entering battle, immediately enters the "Vendetta" state, and lowers the Charge required for "Godslayer Be God" to <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> point(s).

140401.Name: Vow of Voyage
140401.Desc: Deals Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP to one designated enemy.

140402.Name: Deaths are Legion, Regrets are None
140402.Desc: Consumes HP by an amount equal to <unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak> of Mydei's current HP. Deals Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP to one designated enemy and Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP to adjacent targets.\nIf the current HP is not sufficient, using Skill reduces Mydei's current HP to 1.

140403.Name: Throne of Bones
140403.Desc: Restores HP by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[f1]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP and accumulates <unbreak>#5[i]</unbreak> Talent's Charge point(s). Deals Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP to one designated enemy, and deals Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP to adjacent targets. Additionally, Taunts the target and targets adjacent to it, lasting for <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> turn(s). The next use of "Godslayer Be God" prioritizes attacking one designated enemy, and this effect only works on the latest target.

140404.Name: Blood for Blood
140404.Desc: For each 1% of HP lost, accumulates 1 point of Charge (up to <unbreak>200</unbreak> points). When Charge reaches <unbreak>100</unbreak>, consumes <unbreak>100</unbreak> points of Charge to enter the "Vendetta" state, restores HP equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP, and advances action by <unbreak>100%</unbreak>. While the "Vendetta" state is active, Max HP increases by <unbreak>#5[i]%</unbreak> of the current Max HP and DEF remains at 0. At the start of this unit's turn, automatically uses "Kingslayer Be King."\nWhen Charge reaches <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> points during the "Vendetta" state, Mydei immediately gains 1 <u>extra turn</u> and automatically uses "Godslayer Be God."\nWhen receiving a killing blow during the "Vendetta" state, Mydei will not be <u>knocked down</u>, but will clear his Charge, exits the "Vendetta" state, and restores HP by <unbreak>#4[i]%</unbreak> of his Max HP.

140406.Name: Attack
140406.Desc: Attacks an enemy, and when the battle starts, reduces their Toughness of the corresponding Type.

140407.Name: Cage of Broken Lance
140407.Desc: After using Technique, pulls in enemies within a certain area and inflicts Daze on them for <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> second(s). Dazed enemies will not actively attack ally targets.\nIf actively attacking Dazed enemies, when entering battle, deals Imaginary DMG equal to <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> of Mydei's Max HP to all enemies, and Taunts the targets, lasting for <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> turn(s). This unit accumulates <unbreak>#5[i]</unbreak> point(s) of Talent's Charge.

140409.Name: Kingslayer Be King
140409.Desc: Consumes HP by an amount equal to <unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak> of Mydei's current HP. Deals Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP to one enemy and Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP to adjacent targets.\nIf the current HP is not sufficient, using Skill reduces Mydei's current HP to 1.\nThis ability will be automatically used.

140411.Name: Godslayer Be God
140411.Desc: Consumes <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> point(s) of Charge. Deals Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP to one enemy and Imaginary DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of Mydei's Max HP to adjacent targets.\nThis ability will be automatically used. While this ability is in use, Charge cannot be accumulated.

1.PointDesc: During the "Vendetta" state, Mydei will not exit the "Vendetta" state when receiving a killing blow. This effect can trigger <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> time(s) per battle.
While in the "Vendetta" state, Mydei is immune to <u>Crowd Control debuffs</u>.

When battle starts, if Mydei's Max HP exceeds <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak>, for every <unbreak>100</unbreak> excess HP, Mydei's CRIT Rate increases by <unbreak>#3[f1]%</unbreak>, his Charge ratio from enemy targets' DMG increases by <unbreak>#4[f1]%</unbreak>, and his HP restored when receiving healing increases by <unbreak>#5[f2]%</unbreak>. Up to <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> excess HP can be taken into account for this effect.
